    Class for main game functions, contains ArrayLists for countries

    Player

    ScoringCard
    Extends Card and implements Comparable.
    Side
    The ENUM for Sides in the game, it is used in most classes as an identifier.
    TurnCard
    Turn Card extends Card and implements Comparable
    UICore
    UICore is the base of all UIElements and Interactions with the computer.
